{"tid":2272963,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"無麥卡錫主義，美國晨早俾左膠搞到亡國","createTime":"2020-11-05T11:33:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T20:41:17.000Z","uid":290404,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"59f65b24b9c0a4b3045c4de0506773d19e13376b","tid":2272963,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T11:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/8b/Joseph_McCarthy_adjusted.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F8%2F8b%2FJoseph_McCarthy_adjusted.jpg&h=e231d3bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當年蘇聯對美國既滲透不知幾嚴重，如果唔係麥卡錫清查美國國內共產主義，將果d共產黨員送去坐監，美國一早已經成為蘇聯既附庸國家，可能美國今日會幫中共踩埋手足一腳都唔奇。<br />\n<br />\n再講，就算有人吹水吹到話麥卡錫有殺過人，相比中共、蘇聯同佢地d跟班呢幾十年殺左既人，麥卡錫殺既人連零頭都冇！<br />\n<br />\n美國人係好應該多謝麥卡錫當年既努力！麥卡錫係現代美國自由民主之父！<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"blue\">All American people should thank to Senator Joseph McCarthy!!</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"4e530c54b5a42bc60a5de09b56fbf2ed86fd62fb","tid":2272963,"uid":282494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T06:28:00.000Z","msg":"香港都多漢奸共匪"},{"pid":"8f52045590c88cc0094a3da66fdeb5ec85f03f73","tid":2272963,"uid":290404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4e530c54b5a42bc60a5de09b56fbf2ed86fd62fb","tid":2272963,"uid":282494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T06:28:00.000Z","msg":"香港都多漢奸共匪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T09:19:42.000Z","msg":"美國仲多，所以美國需要麥卡錫主義"},{"pid":"9855d60b18f5300a144956409f0d7064411f7131","tid":2272963,"uid":364798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T09:22:57.000Z","msg":"好有霸氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30db